name: Jaywalking - The Software
description: The software behind the "Jaywalking Frames" project. "Jaywalking Frames" are images from people walking trough a red light. The price = fine for jaywalking. The image is captured with the use of unprotected CCTV camera and computer vision software by Belgium artist Dries Depoorter @driesdepoorter. This time the money doesn't go the the police but do an artist.
